title: You’re Doing Amazing Sweetie: A Kardashian Recap Show | It Was All A Stream
description:
On this week's episode, Amelia Wedemeyer and Zack Peter dive into Episode 6 of ‘The Kardashians.’ They break down Kourtney’s Las Vegas wedding (11:00), Kim’s star-studded Skims icon photo shoot (18:00), as well as some notable show superlatives (43:00).
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Zack Peter
Producer: Devon Renaldo
